                     <interp inst="t17840915-155-off715" type="offenceCategory" value="royalOffences"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17840915-155-off715" type="offenceSubcategory" value="coiningOffences"></interp>
               that he, on the <rs id="t17840915-155-cd716" type="crimeDate">7th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17840915-155-off715 t17840915-155-cd716"></join> last, one piece of false and counterfeit money and coin, made and counterfeited to the likeness and similitude of a shilling, did offer to one 
                     
                        <persName id="t17840915-155-victim1345" type="victimName">
                           Edward 
                           West
                        <interp inst="t17840915-155-victim1345" type="surname" value="West"></interp>
